data.description: ***OPEN HOUSE THIS SUNDAY 2/25, 12PM - 3PM*** PRICED TO SELL!!! GORGEOUS HOME LOCATED IN ASTORIA TRAILS GATED COMMUNITY IN THE NORTHWEST! FRESHLY PAINTED THROUGHOUT AND MOVE IN READY! THE HOME FEATURES 3 BEDROOMS A DEN AND LOFT! OPEN KITCHEN CONCEPT WITH LARGE GREAT ROOM AND DINING ROOM COMBINED FOR MAXIMUM USE OF SPACE. TONS OF NATURAL LIGHT AND BACKYARD LARGE ENOUGH FOR A POOL! VAULTED CEILINGS AND KITCHEN ISLAND WITH GRANITE COUNTERTOPS AND LARGE PANTRY. THIS GEM ALSO FEATURES A SMALL DEN DOWNSTAIRS AND LOFT UPSTAIRS. THE COMMUNITY HAS A PARK WITH PLAYGROUND AND VOLLEYBALL COURT. WELCOME HOME!
